line_2: Just serves to shew how much she wants.

line_1: To me perhaps kind heav'n indulgent grants
line_2: The spirits, health, or limbs my neighbour wants;

line_1: This humble prayer gay Flora grants,
line_2: For soon supply'd are little wants;

line_1: They barter Places, and dispose of Grants,
line_2: Whole Provinces unequal to their Wants.
